output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. Has CMF: No visible CMF number, but this doesn't automatically disqualify it as propaganda.
2. Refers to candidate: Yes, explicitly mentions "George Simion PREȘEDINTE" in the link title, who is a presidential candidate (Position 2 on the official list).
3. Addresses wide population: Yes, this is a paid advertisement reaching between 45,000-49,999 impressions, clearly intended for mass distribution.
4. Electoral objective: Yes, clear electoral objective: - Directly promotes George Simion for president - Uses campaign-specific language ("șansa unică de a schimba") - Calls for electoral action against established parties - The link title explicitly asks "De ce e nevoie de George Simion PREȘEDINTE?"
5. Journalism: No, this is not journalistic content. It's campaign material promoting a specific candidate.
6. Personal opinion: No, this is structured campaign messaging with paid distribution.
This is clearly electoral propaganda for the presidential election, which is not allowed after the campaign period has ended.

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post constitutes electoral propaganda because: - Explicitly promotes a presidential candidate - Has clear electoral messaging - Uses paid distribution to reach a wide audience - Aims to influence voting behavior - Directly related to the presidential campaign
conclusion.message-for-police: AUR - Sălașu de Sus, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin promovarea unui mesaj de propaganda electorala pentru candidatul George Nicolae Simion la functia de presedinte al Romaniei, dupa incheierea perioadei de campanie electorala. Postarea cu ID-ul 932890622061028, publicata si promovata dupa ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, contine mesaje directe de sustinere electorala ("De ce e nevoie de George Simion PREȘEDINTE?"), indeamna explicit la schimbarea conducerii tarii prin vot ("șansa unică de a schimba cu adevărat această țară"), si a fost distribuita prin reclama platita pe Facebook si Instagram, atingand intre 45.000 si 50.000 de impresii, demonstrand astfel intentia clara de a influenta comportamentul electoral al alegatorilor in perioada in care propaganda electorala este interzisa prin lege.
